     Geant4 - an Object-Oriented Toolkit for Simulation in HEP
     =========================================================

                            Simpit
                            ----------
 	Simpit based on Geant4, a simple program simulates positron source for ILC
	In Simpit 1.4 all units will use standardize to kg, m, s, include implemented classes and methods.
